getComponentCount().Description: Returns the number of components for this color model.

ClassDesc: A color model is required by a @B_android#graphics#ColorSpace_E@ to describe the way colors can be represented as tuples of numbers. A common color model is the @B_android#graphics#ColorSpace#Model#RGB_E@ color model which defines a color as represented by a tuple of 3 numbers (red, green and blue).
